# Changelog

All notable changes to the Praxxys Nuxt 3 Boilerplate will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.1.0] - 2024-11-18

### Added
- Initial project structure and configuration
- Core features:
  - TypeScript integration with strict mode
  - shadcn-ui component library setup
  - ESLint and Prettier configuration
  - Husky pre-commit hooks
  - Vitest testing infrastructure
  
- Performance optimizations:
  - Image optimization with @nuxt/image
  - Font optimization with @nuxtjs/fontaine
  - CSS optimization with @nuxtjs/critters
  - Hydration optimization with nuxt-delay-hydration
  
- Developer experience:
  - VS Code configuration
  - Type checking setup
  - Hot Module Replacement
  - Development tools and debugging support

- Documentation:
  - Project structure guide
  - Development guidelines
  - Component standards
  - README with quick start guide

### Security
- Environment variable validation
- Secure headers configuration
- CORS policy setup
- Referrer policy implementation

## [Unreleased]
Planned features and improvements for future releases:

### Upcoming
- Authentication module integration
- Error handling system
- API integration examples
- E2E testing setup
- CI/CD pipeline configuration
- Storybook integration for component documentation

---

Note: This CHANGELOG will be updated as new versions are released. Each version should include the following categories when applicable:
- Added - for new features
- Changed - for changes in existing functionality
- Deprecated - for soon-to-be removed features
- Removed - for now removed features
- Fixed - for any bug fixes
- Security - in case of vulnerabilities